'''Ryll kor''' was the rarest grade of [[Ryll/Legends|ryll]]. It made up approximately three percent of all ryll<ref name="TCSWE">{{CSWECite|II|226|kor}}</ref>. Ryll kor absorbed light except in the [[Ultraviolet/Legends|ultraviolet]] range. [[Airen Cracken/Legends|Airen Cracken]] possesed gear that was able to sort true ryll kor from other grades of ryll that had been dyed [[Color/Legends|black]].<ref name="TKT" /> 

When the [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] population was afflicted with the [[Krytos virus]], Ryll kor was combined with [[Bacta/Legends|bacta]] to create [[rylca]] as a cure for the virus.<ref name="TKT">''[[X-Wing: The Krytos Trap]]''</ref>

